Services

Services

Services

What we do

PrimoVac offers vacuum pump inspection, servicing, overhaul, sales, and spare partsincluding Medical Vacuum Systems (Duplex and Triplex systems)

Vacuum Pump Inspection

PrimoVac offers thorough inspection services to detect early signs of wear, leakage, or inefficiency in your vacuum systems. Our process includes detailed diagnostics and performance assessments to ensure smooth operation.

Service & Maintenance

We provide comprehensive service and preventive maintenance tailored to your vacuum pump's make and model. Our technicians handle cleaning, lubrication, filter replacement, and system performance.

Overhaul & Repair

PrimoVac handles complete overhaul and precise repairs to bring worn-out pumps back to optimal performance. From part replacements to assembling of pump, we restore every component to manufacturer standards.

New Pump Sales

We supply a wide range of high-performance vacuum pumps suited for various industrial applications. Our team helps you select the right model based on your capacity, budget, and system needs. All new units are backed by warranty and technical support.

Spare Parts & Vacuum Oils

PrimoVac offers genuine spare parts and premium vacuum oils from trusted suppliers to keep your systems running efficiently. We ensure compatibility with leading pump brands and offer fast delivery to reduce downtime. Proper parts and fluids play a crucial role in maintaining vacuum performance and longevity.

Services for Duplex, Triplex Systems & More

We specialize in servicing multi-pump systems including Duplex, Triplex, and custom configurations. Our solutions include synchronization, load balancing, and individual unit diagnostics. This ensures optimal performance, energy efficiency, and system reliability across all units.

Rotary Vane Vacuum Pump (Oil-Lubricated)

Reliable and efficient, oil-lubricated rotary vane vacuum pumps are widely used in industrial and laboratory settings. They offer high pumping speed and deep ultimate vacuum, ideal for applications like freeze-drying, vacuum distillation, and analytical instrumentation.

Claw Vacuum Pump (Dry)

Dry claw vacuum pumps are known for their reliability and efficiency in various industrial applications. These pumps offer a contact-free operation, ensuring a clean vacuum without the need for oil or other sealing fluids. They are commonly used in packaging, plastics, and environmental technologies.

Medical Vacuum System

A critical component in healthcare facilities, a medical vacuum system provides reliable, continuous vacuum for various clinical applications. These systems are essential for surgical procedures, wound drainage, suctioning, and other medical interventions, ensuring patient safety and operational efficiency within hospitals and clinics.

What area are you based in?

We're based in Karachi and primarily serve the surrounding areas but our work doesnt stop there. Over the years, weve had the opportunity to collaborate with clients across Pakistan, from major cities to smaller towns.

Do you offer free quotes?

Yes! We offer free, no-obligation quotes. After an initial consultation, well assess your project needs and provide a detailed estimate so you know exactly what to expect.

Do you provide a guarantee for your work?

Absolutely! We stand by the quality of our craftsmanship and offer guarantees on our work to give you peace of mind. Specific warranties may vary depending on the type of projectjust ask us for details.

How do I get started with a project?
